Feature: 契約 PDF 產生
  對應模組：後端 ContractController / ContractService / PdfGenerator
  API 基礎路徑：/api/contracts
  PDF 模板：唯讀，不得修改
  PDF 輸出：generated-contracts/ 目錄

  Background:
    Given 系統已啟動且資料目錄已建立
    And PDF 模板檔案存在於 settings.json 設定的路徑
    And owners.json 中已有飼主 "owner_001"（王小明），資料如下：
      """
      {
        "id": "owner_001",
        "name": "王小明",
        "nationalId": "A123456789",
        "phone": "0912345678",
        "address": "桃園市桃園區中正路1號",
        "emergencyContactName": "王太太",
        "emergencyContactPhone": "0987654321",
        "emergencyContactRelationship": "配偶",
        "isStoredValueCustomer": true,
        "storedValueBalance": 5000
      }
      """
    And pets.json 中已有寵物 "pet_001"（Lucky），資料如下：
      """
      {
        "id": "pet_001",
        "ownerId": "owner_001",
        "name": "Lucky",
        "species": "犬",
        "breed": "貴賓",
        "gender": "公",
        "age": "3歲",
        "isNeutered": true,
        "chipNumber": "900000000012345",
