        "physicalExamination": { "eyes": "正常", "ears": "正常", "teeth": "正常", "limbs": "正常", "skin": "正常", "fur": "正常" },
        "medicalHistory": []
      }
      """
    And grooming-records.json 中已有紀錄 "rec_001"，appointmentId: "appt_001", services: [{"item": "洗澡", "price": 500}]

  # ===================================================================
  # 後端 - 成功產生契約
  # ===================================================================

  @backend @unit-test
  Scenario: 後端 - 成功產生契約 PDF
    When 呼叫 POST "/api/contracts/generate" 並帶入以下 JSON：
      """
      { "recordId": "rec_001" }
      """
    Then 回應狀態碼應為 201
    And 回應 JSON 應包含：
      | 欄位            | 說明                                     |
      | contractPath    | PDF 檔案路徑                             |
      | version         | 版本編號                                 |
      | generatedAt     | 產生時間（ISO 8601）                     |
      | generatedBy     | 產生者名稱                               |
    And generated-contracts/ 目錄下應存在新的 PDF 檔案
    And grooming-records.json 中 "rec_001" 的 contractPaths 應包含該 PDF 路徑
    And grooming-records.json 中 "rec_001" 應記錄 contractGeneratedAt 和 contractGeneratedBy

